        <div class="text-xs text-[#FCAD2A] font-mono mb-3">SYNAPSE DAILY INTELLIGENCE · 2026-04-12</div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="shrink-0 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#0A1628] bg-[#FCAD2A] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">HIGH</span><span class="text-xs text-white/60">Harness Engineering formalized as the 2026 AI engineering paradigm</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="shrink-0 text-[10px] font-bold text-white bg-[#028CDC] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">MED</span><span class="text-xs text-white/60">Multi-agent enterprise adoption up 327% YoY</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2 items-start"><span class="shrink-0 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#0A1628] bg-[#FCAD2A] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">HIGH</span><span class="text-xs text-white/60">Claude Code Scheduled Tasks now generally available</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono">Reviewed by Graphify Think Tank · 3 findings · 2 high priority</div>
